ord!</span><br />\n<br />\n認真求推,搞左呢份野等三萬黑警都要接受國際審判<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1617815\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1617815</a>"},{"pid":"1122248efbe897800a529a03ee735886b3de77f1","tid":1641801,"uid":130079,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-12T13:42:43.000Z","msg":"Finally we have a good one"},{"pid":"9f3e4ec2a807273e7587d7ea39f41eb33016170e","tid":1641801,"uid":322412,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-12T13:58:36.000Z","msg":"推<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"fd1b7d50369c8d163a2d32fe706a9a816239ab77","tid":1641801,"uid":108757,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-12T14:13:21.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\nworld toi don't have ppl"},{"pid":"fafb977a9ad53243f902c3a13d85adfcbb9cd8c1","tid":1641801,"uid":77905,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-12T14:20:54.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">Twitter英文文宣：警察嚴重罪案一覽</span><br />\n同我推爆Twitter佢<br />\n<br />\nPAGE1<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/PfV2ooj.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FPfV2ooj.png&h=e063d212&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\nPAGE2<br />\n <img src=\"https://na.cx/i/V2Xj93k.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FV2Xj93k.png&h=16186fcf&s={SIZE}\" /> <br />\n<br />\nquote晒新聞出處, 內文亦係新聞cap. <br />\n藍絲五毛即管fact check<br />\n<br />\n警隊近年無論在當值或休班, 犯罪率不斷攀升<br />\n示威時被拍攝到各種暴力, 性罪行, 插贓嫁禍, <br />\n只不過係過往一連串警隊管理問題的前身<br />\n<br />\n2008 旺角警署強姦案<br />\n2012 的士司機遭警箍頸後癱瘓亡<br />\n2015 CID涉警總摸女醫生胸 搜身看私處兩秒<br />\n2016 已婚警長涉非禮性騷擾兩女同袍, 警署警長涉非禮及襲擊女同袍<br />\n2018 捲非禮女童遭停職男警再涉梯間強暴14歲女<br />\n2019 六旬老翁醫院內疑遭警員私刑<br />\n<br />\n一切一切事件作為背景, 加上示威大家有眼見嘅呢一切<br />\n重組警隊，刻不容緩"},{"pid":"f2370af57fc24f331ea9fed7e322791f36b245b0","tid":1641801,"uid":57141,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2